# BLOG SİSTEMİ BACKEND RAPORU

## Teknoloji Stack

### Dil: Java 21
### Framework: Spring Boot 3
### Build Tool: Maven
### ORM: Hibernate
### Repository Katmanı: Spring Data JPA
### Database: PostgreSQL
### Migration: Flyway
### Authentication: Spring Security
### Authorization: JWT + HttpOnly Cookie
### API Dokümantasyonu: Swagger/OpenAPI
### Arama: Elasticsearch
### Dosya Depolama: MinIO / Cloudflare R2
### Container: Docker

